---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Jack" description="Learn about Jack McGhee's journey from Sydney's competitive markets to the Sunshine Coast">
  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <hgroup>
        <h1>About Jack McGhee</h1>
        <p>"Think you know property? You don't know Jack."</p>
      </hgroup>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid">
        <div>
          <figure class="image-placeholder">
            <span>Jack McGhee</span>
          </figure>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2>A Journey of Excellence</h2>
          <p>
            I'm Jack McGhee, a senior real estate professional with over 20 years of experience 
            delivering premium results in Sydney's most competitive property markets. My career has 
            spanned the Inner City through to the Eastern Beaches, where I've consistently achieved 
            record prices by combining disciplined strategy with decisive negotiation.
          </p>
          <p>
            My approach is grounded in understanding buyer behaviour‚Äîhow people make decisions, 
            what creates urgency, and how to position a property to maximise perceived value. I pair 
            this with clear communication, deep market knowledge, and a calm, down-to-earth style that 
            keeps my clients informed, confident, and in control throughout the process.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2>From Sydney to the Sunshine Coast</h2>
      <p>
        After relocating to the Sunshine Coast with my young family, I'm now proud to call 
        Mooloolaba home and bring metropolitan expertise to a community I've long admired. My focus 
        is simple: reduce uncertainty, protect your property's value, and deliver results that 
        exceed expectations.
      </p>
      <p>
        12 months ago, I settled in Mooloolaba, turning my frequent visits to the Sunshine Coast 
        over the past 15 years into a permanent lifestyle. With strong family ties in Buderim and 
        Mooloolaba, I bring a personal passion for the area alongside my professional expertise 
        honed in Sydney's competitive eastern suburbs.
      </p>
      <p>
        The Sunshine Coast isn't just where I work‚Äîit's the place I call home. Let me help you make 
        this stunning region your home too.
      </p>

      <h2>My Approach</h2>
      <div class="grid">
        <article class="approach-card">
          <h4>üéØ Understanding Buyer Behaviour</h4>
          <p>
            Success in real estate comes from understanding how people make decisions. I focus on 
            what creates urgency and how to position a property to maximise its perceived value.
          </p>
        </article>
        <article class="approach-card">
          <h4>üí¨ Clear Communication</h4>
          <p>
            I believe in keeping my clients informed every step of the way. My calm, down-to-earth 
            style ensures you stay confident and in control throughout the process.
          </p>
        </article>
        <article class="approach-card">
          <h4>üìä Deep Market Knowledge</h4>
          <p>
            With 20+ years spanning Sydney's competitive markets and now the Sunshine Coast, I bring 
            data-driven insights that protect your property's value.
          </p>
        </article>
        <article class="approach-card">
          <h4>ü§ù Disciplined Strategy</h4>
          <p>
            Combining strategic marketing with decisive negotiation, I've consistently achieved 
            record prices by reducing uncertainty and delivering exceptional results.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>

      <h2>How I Can Help You</h2>
      
      <article>
        <h3>Selling Your Property</h3>
        <h5>The Power of Emotional Connection</h5>
        <p>
          Australians are motivated by the lifestyle a property offers. My marketing strategies tap 
          into these motivations using tailored storytelling, evocative imagery, and immersive 
          campaigns that make buyers see themselves living in your home.
        </p>
        <h5>Proven Negotiation Expertise</h5>
        <p>
          Maximizing value requires deep market knowledge and strategic insight. I use data-driven 
          approaches to position your property competitively while my negotiation skills ensure you 
          secure the best possible price.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article>
        <h3>Thinking of Buying?</h3>
        <h5>Your Advocate, Every Step of the Way</h5>
        <p>
          Moving to the Sunshine Coast is a life-changing decision, and I'm here to smooth the 
          process. Whether you're relocating from across Australia or looking for an upgrade locally, 
          I understand what matters most‚Äîlocation, lifestyle, and long-term value.
        </p>
        <h5>Market Insights You Can Trust</h5>
        <p>
          I combine hyperlocal knowledge with property-specific insights, ensuring you buy with 
          confidence in one of the fastest-growing regions in the country. From Mooloolaba's relaxed 
          beachside charm to Maroochydore's dynamic community feel, I have you covered.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="cta-section">
        <h2>Ready to Get Started?</h2>
        <p>
          Whether you're buying, selling, or seeking honest market guidance, my goal is to provide 
          a structured, transparent, and highly personalised real estate experience‚Äîmaking your next 
          move both rewarding and seamless.
        </p>
        <a href="#contact" role="button">Contact Jack Today</a>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    /* Page-specific styles for about page */
    .about-hero {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--ocean-deep) 0%, var(--ocean-blue) 100%);
      color: var(--white);
      padding: 4rem 0;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: -1px;
    }

    .about-hero h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      color: var(--white);
    }

    .about-hero p {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      color: var(--gold-light);
      font-family: var(--font-serif);
      font-style: italic;
    }

    .image-placeholder {
      aspect-ratio: 3/4;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--ocean-blue) 0%, var(--ocean-light) 100%);
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: var(--white);
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-family: var(--font-serif);
      margin: 0;
    }

    .approach-card {
      background: var(--sand-warm);
      border-left: 4px solid var(--gold-accent);
      margin: 0;
    }

    .cta-section {
      background: var(--sand-warm);
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .about-hero h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }

      .about-hero p {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
